  "title": "Core Concepts of Sourcing Authentic Thai Ingredients",
  "lessonText": "Understanding where to source authentic Thai ingredients is crucial for creating genuine Thai dishes.",
  "data": {
    "content": "To create authentic Thai cuisine, sourcing the right ingredients is essential. Here are key points to consider:\n\n- **Local Markets:** Visit local Asian markets for fresh produce and specialty items.\n- **Online Resources:** Utilize online retailers that specialize in Thai ingredients.\n- **Quality Matters:** Look for high-quality palm sugar, fish sauce, and fresh herbs to enhance flavors.\n- **Seasonality:** Be aware of seasonal ingredients to ensure freshness and authenticity.\n- **Community Connections:** Engage with local Thai communities for recommendations on sourcing ingredients."
  }
